IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SYSTEM-E2E.

DATA DIVISION.
01 VAL PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 MSG PICTURE IS X(10).
01 IDX PICTURE IS 9(2).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 10 TO VAL
    MOVE "STDOUT" TO MSG
    
    DISPLAY "E2E START"
    DISPLAY "MSG IS: " MSG
    
    IF VAL > 5 THEN
        DISPLAY "IF THEN BLOCK"
    ELSE
        DISPLAY "IF ELSE BLOCK"
    END
    
    LOOP VARYING IDX FROM 1 TO 3 BY 1
        DISPLAY "LOOP IDX: " IDX
    END
    
    EVALUATE VAL
        WHEN 5 THROUGH 15
            DISPLAY "EVALUATE MATCH"
        WHEN OTHER
            DISPLAY "EVALUATE OTHER"
    END
    
    PERFORM SECTION1.

SECTION1.
    DISPLAY "IN SECTION1".
